snippet.title: The Ourobros King - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
The Ouroboros King is a chess-based roguelike, with deep strategic play and lots of different options in the form of new pieces, relics and consumable items.
Get The Ouroboros King:
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2096510/The_Ouroboros_King/
Android - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.OriolCospGames.OuroborosKingChessRoguelike
iOS - https://apps.apple.com/us/app/the-ouroboros-king/id6465395239?platform=iphone
